name: Tez Dizpenser ⁄ Mars ⁄ SYSTEMA SOLARIS ⁄ #6
description: Meet Mars. SYSTEMA SOLARIS is a series of 10 works that captures the sheer beauty and size of our solar system. Each unique 1 of 1 Tez Dizpenser showcases that celestial body's scale, moon(s), rings, color and its distant view of the sun. Join me on this space-bound voyage. Collect them all! 〔 Diameter: 4,221 mi 〕〔 Length of Day: 24.7 hr 〕〔 Distance from Sun: 143 million mi 〕〔 Average Temperature: -85°F 〕〔 Number of Moons: 2 〕 Twitter: @cmilburndesign – Clubhouse: @codestrong
